I agree, when sperm and egg come together there is nothing else needed to determine whether it will grow to be a human or not. The DNA is set for that person forever. The only thing left is growth. Just as a baby from one month to one year living in his natural environment will grow, so does a baby from conception to nine months grow in his natural environment, the womb.Question: Why is it considered a double murder in our law when a woman pregnant with child is killed?